flavor":[{"version":"ruby","text":"Normally, WHISMUR\u2019s voice is very quiet - it is barely audible even if one is paying close attention. However, if this POK\u00e9MON senses danger, it starts crying at an earsplitting volume."},{"version":"sapphire","text":"WHISMUR is very timid. If it starts to cry loudly, it becomes startled by its own crying and cries even harder. When it finally stops crying, the POK\u00e9MON goes to sleep, all tired out."},{"version":"emerald","text":"Its cries equal a jet plane in volume. It inhales through its ear canals. Because of this system, it can cry continually without having to catch its breath."},{"version":"firered","text":"It usually murmurs, but starts crying loudly if it senses danger. It stops when its ear covers are shut."},{"version":"leafgreen","text":"It usually murmurs, but starts crying loudly if it senses danger. It stops when its ear covers are shut."},{"version":"diamond","text":"Usually, its cries are like quiet murmurs. If frightened, it shrieks at the same volume as a jet plane."},{"version":"pearl","text":"Usually, its cries are like quiet murmurs. If frightened, it shrieks at the same volume as a jet plane."},{"version":"platinum","text":"Usually, its cries are like quiet murmurs. If frightened, it shrieks at the same volume as a jet plane."},{"version":"heartgold","text":"If it senses danger, it scares the foe by crying out with the volume of a jet-plane engine."},{"version":"soulsilver","text":"If it senses danger, it scares the foe by crying out with the volume of a jet-plane engine."},{"version":"black","text":"Usually, its cries are like quiet murmurs. If frightened, it shrieks at the same volume as a jet plane."},{"version":"white","text":"Usually, its cries are like quiet murmurs. If frightened, it shrieks at the same volume as a jet plane."},{"version":"black-2","text":"Usually, its cries are like quiet murmurs. If frightened, it shrieks at the same volume as a jet plane."},{"version":"white-2","text":"Usually, its cries are like quiet murmurs. If frightened, it shrieks at the same volume as a jet plane."},{"version":"x","text":"It usually murmurs but starts crying loudly if it senses danger. It stops when its ear covers are shut."},{"version":"y","text":"If it senses danger, it scares the foe by crying out with the volume of a jet-plane engine."},{"version":"omega-ruby","text":"Normally, Whismur\u2019s voice is very quiet\u2014it is barely audible even if one is paying close attention. However, if this Pok\u00e9mon senses danger, it starts crying at an earsplitting volume."},{"version":"alpha-sapphire","text":"Whismur is very timid. If it starts to cry loudly, it becomes startled by its own crying and cries even harder. When it finally stops crying, the Pok\u00e9mon goes to sleep, all tired out."},{"version":"sword","text":"The cry of a Whismur is over 100 decibels. If you\u2019re close to a Whismur when it lets out a cry, you\u2019ll be stuck with an all-day headache."},{"version":"shield","text":"When Whismur cries, the sound of its own voice startles it, making the Pok\u00e9mon cry even louder. It cries until it\u2019s exhausted, then it falls asleep."}],"evo":{"name":"whismur","level":0,"min_level":null,"trigger":null,"item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":null,"turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"loudred","level":1,"min_level":20,"trigger":"level-up","item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"","turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"exploud","level":2,"min_level":40,"trigger":"level-up","item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld